This paper is about hyperparameter optimization using Bayesian Optimization over Gaussian Processes. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it is the primary focus of the paper. The other likely categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as these fields often require hyperparameter optimization and use Bayesian Optimization as a method.
